.invitation
  %p
    Get ready for DEF CON Capture The Flag 2017, because this year's game is
    gonna
    rock. We've been putting together all new challenges for players of every
    skill level. We've got quick warm-ups and short ditties for new competitors.
    Experienced players can't rest easy though, because we have sprawling
    prog-rock epic challenges that won't just blow your mind, they'll blow your
    soul.
  %p
    The Final Countdown begins on April 29.
  %table#timetable
    %tbody
      %tr
        %th Qualifications begin
        %td Midnight UTC, April 29
        %td.time_t= game_window.first.to_i
      %tr
        %th Qualifications end
        %td Midnight UTC, May 1
        %td.time_t= game_window.last.to_i
.actions
  .new
    %h1 Register
    %div
      = link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_path, class: 'btn'
  .forgot
    %h1 Forgot Password
    %div
      = link_to 'Reset Password', new_reset_path, class: 'btn'
  .login
    %h1 Log In
    = form_tag session_path do
      %div
        = label_tag :username
        = text_field_tag :username
      %div
        = label_tag :password
        = password_field_tag :password
      %div
        %label &nbsp;
        = submit_tag 'Log In'

- content_for :head do
  %meta(name="twitter:card" content="summary")
  %meta(name="twitter:site" content="@legitbs_ctf")
  %meta(name="twitter:title" content="DEF CON Capture The Flag 2017")
  %meta(name="twitter:description" content="DEF CON CTF is the world series of computer hacking, with qualifications online in May and finals at DEF CON in Las Vegas.")
